data.description: Come On By Saturday 2/24 From 11-2 For an Open House. Wow and a Price Drop! Take a look at this Beautiful, Huge, Mobile Home, sitting on a Double Corner lot with a completely fenced back yard. It is located in a 55+ community with a very small 120/year HOA Fee. The Home comes completely move-in ready, turn-key and furnished. Sellers only taking small personal items. The property has a formal living room and a family room with a wood burning fireplace, nice large kitchen with new dishwasher and new over stove microwave. The kitchen also features a nice walk-in pantry. The property is a split floor plan with three guest rooms on one side and a very large master bedroom on the other. The guest bedrooms are furnished with a queen bed in bedroom 1, a double bed in bedroom 2, and twin beds in bedroom 3. Lots of space for guests. The Master Suite features, a separate reading/office area, extra-large king size bed, 8’x10’ walk in closet. The very large master bathroom features a garden tub, double sinks with a walk-in shower. Some very recent NEW features include New Carpet in the Living room and Family room, New Vinal Plank Flooring in the Kitchen, Dining, and Master Bathroom. The home also has a NEW ROOF in 2018 and a NEW AC. The home is in a very Nice quiet neighborhood only 5 minutes to restaurants, shopping, lakes, golf course and more. This is a MUST-SEE property; it is perfect for a permanent home or winter residence. Extremely well-maintained.
